Shell Script to take backup of multiple folders in one compressed file



#!/bin/bash

#Specify folders whose backup is to be taken in variables
bck1="/home/ubuntu/majedaar/Devops.txt"
bck2="/home/ubuntu/majedaar/devops"

#tar = Tape Archive tool for compression
#Creating same backup tar file for all specified folders
tar -cvf /home/ubuntu/majedaar/multiple_file.tar $bck1 $bck2 


#Show the size of the folder
du -sh

